name: Radio Caca
description:
Radio Caca is a decentralized organization (DAO) operated by
internet-native individuals all over the globe who share a single vision
of building a brave new virtual world. Radio Caca (RACA) is the
exclusive manager of Maye Musk Mystery Box (MPB) NFT. RACA is the native
token for blockchain P2E game Metamon and for the Universal Metaverse
(a.k.a. USM). The Universal Metaverse : A 3D Planet world where users
can own lands, build stores and art galleries, create and play games.
With a Google-Earth-like UX, users will be able to dynamically zoom in
and out and travel around the 3D virtual planet, a first-ever feature in
the game industry globally.
